    SnapshotExecutionEngine
    ExecutionEngine engine that will try to run cypher query with guarantee that query will never see any data that coming from transaction that are newer then transaction that was the last closed on a moment when VersionContext was initialised.
    SystemExecutionEngine
    This class is a specialized form of the ExecutionEngine containing two internal Cypher engines.
